@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam arrowColor #2E5C8A
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #666666
skinparam shadowing false

title 脉冲神经网络 SNN Transformer 架构

rectangle "输入脉冲序列" as Input
rectangle "脉冲编码器" as Encoder
rectangle "脉冲注意力机制" as Attention
rectangle "Add Norm 1" as Norm1
rectangle "脉冲前馈网络" as FFN
rectangle "Add Norm 2" as Norm2
rectangle "脉冲解码器" as Decoder
rectangle "输出预测信号" as Output
rectangle "可塑性模块" as Plasticity

Input --> Encoder : Shape T B C
Encoder --> Attention : 脉冲S
Attention --> Norm1
Norm1 --> FFN
FFN --> Norm2
Norm2 --> Decoder
Decoder --> Output : Shape T B D

Norm2 --> Plasticity : 脉冲时序
Plasticity --> Attention : 权重更新
Plasticity --> FFN : 权重更新

Attention ..> Norm1 : 残差
FFN ..> Norm2 : 残差

note right of Attention
  脉冲注意力特点
  1. 稀疏脉冲计算
  2. 时间维度注意力
  3. 事件驱动激活
end note

note right of FFN
  脉冲神经元方程
  dV/dt 等于负V加输入电流
  当V超过阈值则发放脉冲
end note

note right of Plasticity
  STDP时间窗
  根据脉冲时序差调整权重
  pre先于post则增强
  post先于pre则减弱
end note

@enduml
